snippet.title: TRAGEDY AT LAW by Cyril Hare MURDER FOR PLEASURE | BBC RADIO DRAMA
snippet.description:
TRAGEDY AT LAW by Cyril Hare MURDER FOR PLEASURE | BBC RADIO DRAMA - dramatised for radio by JAMES PICKLES with Benjamin Whitrow as Mr Justice Barber
Mr Justice Barber receives various threats on his life during the course of his circuit. The question is: how seriously should he take them?
Directed by BRIAN MILLER BBC Bristol
(Repeated: Mon 3.0 pm)
